---
description: "File and folder architecture rules for the weather/surf app"
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Main structure: `/src/app`, `/src/components`, `/src/store`, `/src/shared`, `/src/styles`
- Group components by feature (`/forecast`, `/spot`) or type (`/ui`, `/charts`)
- Place API routes in `/pages/api/` or `/app/api/` (Next.js 13+)
- Put generic UI elements in `/components/ui/`, domain-specific in `/components/feature/`
- Store Zustand state logic inside `/src/store`
